vstore.framework.file

Class VStoreFile

  • java.lang.Object
    • vstore.framework.file.VStoreFile
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class VStoreFile
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This class provides a wrapper for files stored and retrieved by the Virtual Storage framework.

    • Constructor Detail

      • VStoreFile

        public VStoreFile(java.lang.String uuid,
                  java.io.File f,
                  java.lang.String descriptiveName,
                  java.lang.String fileType,
                  boolean isUploadPending,
                  boolean isPrivate)
           throws java.io.FileNotFoundException
        Same as the other constructors, but will use the given filename if it is not null.
        Parameters:
        uuid - UUID of the file
        f - The file object
        descriptiveName - The name of the file you want to use.
        fileType - The MIME type (should be from VFileType class)
        isUploadPending - Set it to true if an upload is currently pending for this file.
        isPrivate - Set this to true, if the file is private.
        Throws:
        java.io.FileNotFoundException - Will be thrown if file is not found.

      • VStoreFile

           throws java.io.FileNotFoundException

        isUploadPending - Set this to true if an upload is currently pending for this file.
        isPrivate - Set this to true if the file is private.
        Throws:

      • VStoreFile

        public VStoreFile(java.lang.String uuid,
                  java.lang.String descriptiveName,
                  java.lang.String path,
                  java.lang.String fileType,
                  java.lang.String fileExtension,
                  java.util.Date creationDate,
                  boolean isUploadPending,
                  boolean isPrivate)
           throws java.io.FileNotFoundException
        Most flexible constructor for a vStoreFile.
        Parameters:
        uuid - The UUID of the file
        descriptiveName - "Display name" for the file
        path - Full Absolute Path to the file (without the file name itself and without trailing /)
        fileType - The MIME type (should be from VFileType class)
        fileExtension - Extension of the file (e.g. mp4, jpeg, ...)
        creationDate - Creation Date of the file. If null, now() will be used.
        isUploadPending - Set it to true if an upload is currently pending for this file.
        isPrivate - Set this to true, if the file is private.
        Throws:
        java.io.FileNotFoundException - If the file is not found.
